metadata.name: Colorful Chemistry
metadata.description:
"Colorful Chemistry" was inspired when I was a student majoring in chemistry. I want to share my experience and the colorful beauty of chemistry.

behind the complexity and difficulty of studying the field of chemistry that hidden uniqueness of chemical colors and it is very amazing.

All bidders will receive a stamp and winner collector will receive another version of this illustration and of course also a stamp. thank you^^

1/1 Edition.
